    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. To address common platform weak points, the rear subframe has been reinforced with plates, and the Double VANOS system has been fully overhauled. Recent service includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and rod bearing replacement, ensuring the internal reciprocating assembly remains within spec. The chassis retains its signature balance with refreshed bushings and MacPherson/Multi-link suspension geometry that remains taut and communicative. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain and structural integrity are prioritized for the driver who values performance and engineering over trailer-queen status.",
