    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2018 BMW 540i xDrive is a meticulously maintained executive sedan that perfectly balances athletic performance with refined luxury. The exterior is finished in a sophisticated Bluestone Metallic that still holds a deep, mirror-like gloss. While there are a few minor stone chips on the front valence consistent with careful highway use, the body is free of major dings or scratches. Inside, the Mocha Nappa leather remains supple and rich; the driver\u2019s seat shows only light softening of the bolster, while the passenger and rear seats appear nearly new. This is a non-smoker vehicle with a clean, fresh interior aroma. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health. I have retained a comprehensive folder of all service records, including a recent 60,000-mile major service and the installation of a fresh set of Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. The turbocharged inline-six engine provides smooth, linear power, and the xDrive system ensures confident handling in all weather conditions. The sale includes two key fobs, the original floor mats, and a complete set of owner's manuals. This vehicle has been garaged daily and stands as a prime example of a well-cared-for daily driver.",
